snippet.title: Become A Test Pilot
snippet.description:
A new type of game is being develop by the indie dev 8 Circuit Studios.  Want uber early access to Test Pilot avatars and ship chassis for the space-combat first-person-shooter mash-up Project Genesis?

Sign today at: www.projectgenesis.com
